> hey @qfrank i think we shouldn't "fix" `{"method":{"method"` in status. it should be fixed in the dapp

Hi @flexsurfer , i tried https://connect.collab.land/ with metamask, it doesn't work neither after signed, 
![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/12406719/180919037-f584f2e4-c2bb-4226-a9e8-68c1a56375f1.png)
i think we should fix it in status, make the `signing a message` pop up at least like this: 
![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/12406719/180919413-5db3b4ed-48d3-4dc7-8395-0414423a7bee.png)
Currently, it doesn't even show the `signing a message` when u pressed the button `Sign Message`.

The request param looks weird cause of our implementation for ethereum.send() is not good enough, ethereum.send() can be called in three different ways(reference is [here](https://docs.metamask.io/guide/ethereum-provider.html#legacy-methods)):
```
// 1.
ethereum.send(payload: JsonRpcRequest, callback: JsonRpcCallback): void;

// 2.
ethereum.send(method: string, params?: Array<unknown>): Promise<JsonRpcResponse>;

// 3.
ethereum.send(payload: JsonRpcRequest): unknown;
``` 
current implementation didn't take care of the 1st way neither the 3rd way

